  "detailed_description": "You awaken in Blender's restaurant.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt's dark. The exits are sealed shut. If you explore your surroundings, you will find hidden objects that will unlock various areas around the restaurant. You must keep searching until you find your way out. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nBe careful. Blenderman lurks in the shadows. He doesn't get company often. He wants to keep you til dinner time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n...You do not want to stay for dinner.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt's 1 o' clock. You have 5 hours to escape before you get eaten by Blender.",
